<p>Hasta ahora nuestro tema se ve así:</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-812" alt="tema-wp-2-3" src="http://franciscoamk.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/tema-wp-2-3-1024x962.png" width="980" height="920" srcset="https://franciscoamk.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/tema-wp-2-3-1024x962.png 1024w, https://franciscoamk.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/tema-wp-2-3-319x300.png 319w" sizes="(max-width: 980px) 100vw, 980px" /></p>
